* _the eigenvalue of_ \(V\) _with largest modulus is real, positive, and simple; namely,_ \[_{1}(V)>|_{2}(V)||_{d}(V)|.\]
* \( Q_{1},K_{1}>0\) _for any_ \(_{1}^{d}\) _lying on the line_ \((V-_{1}(V)I_{d})\)_._

